column2: select   m.mangaid, m.ra as ra1, m.dec as dec1, n.objid, z.nvote, z.p_el as elliptical, z.p_cw as spiralclock,   z.p_acw as spiralanticlock, z.p_edge as edgeon, z.p_dk as dontknow, z.p_mg as merger  from MyDB.MyTable as m      cross apply dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(m.ra, m.dec,#) as n   join DR8.ZooSpec as z on n.objid=z.objid   where m.mangaid=&&&
